title: S16 Ep42: Life, The Afterlife & Beyond w/ Denise Marie
itunes:title: Life, The Afterlife & Beyond w/ Denise Marie
description:
Darkness Radio presents Life, The Afterlife & Beyond with guest Denise Marie

Dave & Tim are joined by renowned psychic medium Denise Marie to hear her stories of growing up gifted with the ability to see and communicate with the dead. Denise Marie's abilities go back to age 4 and she is a sought after speaker, teacher and Medium with insights into Life, Death and The Great Beyond, we also discuss children with gifts and dealing with ghosts.

Visit Denise Marie here. www.HaloReadings.com

Visit Denise Marie's YouTube Channel here: https://bit.ly/328dfFj
